events.title: MAPS-MCRC: Ramadhan Food Drive
events.description: MAPS-MCRC, in partnership with Masajids in the Seattle area, will be delivering care boxes of food to needy Muslim families in our community so that they can enjoy a blessed and peaceful Ramadan.Each box will include food staples such as rice, oil, lentils, dates, sugar, etc., sufficient for a family of 5 for one month.You can sponsor one or more boxes ($60/box)
